Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就随它去吧。\N{\rENG}I'm just gonna go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一头猪。\N{\rENG}I was a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是库斯已经走了;我不知道该怎么处理这些破事。\N{\rENG}But Cus was gone; I didn't know how to deal with all that shit.
