Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样，迈克。\N{\rENG}INTERVIEWER: Come on, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说没有一百万个女孩\N{\rENG}You mean there aren't a million girls
