Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只想要现金。\N{\rENG}They just want the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有几百万美元可以花。\N{\rENG}Got millions of dollars to spend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱一个那样的人很容易。\N{\rENG}It's easy to love someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我长什么样。\N{\rENG}You know, I know what I look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都在镜子里看到自己。\N{\rENG}20.\N{\rENG}I see myself in the mirror every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，但是，我只是希望\N{\rENG}Nah, but, you know, I just wish
