Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还以为我是个好人\N{\rENG}and just thought I was a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能背叛过每一个和我在一起的女人。\N{\rENG}I probably cheated on every woman I ever been with.
