Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(观众窃窃私语)\N{\rENG}[audience murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，听着，我们都是婴儿。\N{\rENG}Listen, listen, we were babies.
