Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她很漂亮。\N{\rENG}I thought she was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，看看她。\N{\rENG}I mean, look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个漂亮的女孩，对吧?\N{\rENG}She's a beautiful girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能得到的。\N{\rENG}Unobtainable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去追她。\N{\rENG}So I went after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了她。\N{\rENG}I tracked her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费了点功夫，但我给我们定了个约会。\N{\rENG}Took a little work, but I set up a date for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，在我的脑海里，就像\N{\rENG}You know, in my head, it was like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在演我自己的浪漫喜剧。\N{\rENG}I was in my own version of a fucking rom-com.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(欢快的音乐)\N{\rENG}[upbeat music]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾令人印象深刻。\N{\rENG}Robin was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时电视上很少有年轻的黑人女性。\N{\rENG}There were very few young Black women on TV back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是一个榜样，那个it girl。\N{\rENG}She was a role model, the it girl.
