Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为那种人\N{\rENG}I wanted to be the kind of person
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾最想爱上的人。\N{\rENG}Robin would wanna fall in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手:\N{\rENG}你问什么都行\N{\rENG}SINGERS:\N{\rENG}Anything you ask
