Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸对她的出轨太严重了，\N{\rENG}My dad cheated on her so bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她只是想确认一下\N{\rENG}so she was just trying to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以自立了。\N{\rENG}I could stand on my own two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不太了解我妈。\N{\rENG}- I didn't really know my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟她说过话\N{\rENG}I didn't have any conversations with her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像那样，就像我对库斯那样。\N{\rENG}like that, like I did with Cus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有很多事想问她。\N{\rENG}There's a lot I wish I could ask her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是啊，我是说\N{\rENG}- Mm, yeah, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不了解我爸爸。\N{\rENG}I still don't know my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得，如果我不是\N{\rENG}I always felt like, you know, if I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够聪明够漂亮还是…\N{\rENG}smart enough or pretty enough or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好到让我爸爸爱我，\N{\rENG}good enough for my dad to love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有人爱我?\N{\rENG}why would anyone love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会想到，看看我们，我们也有同样的问题?\N{\rENG}Who would think, to look at us, that we got the same problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[瓶子碰碰声][两人轻笑]\N{\rENG}[bottles clink] [both chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不，你太美了。\N{\rENG}- No, you are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不可怜。\N{\rENG}- I'm not pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我说的是"美"不是"可怜"\N{\rENG}- I said "beautiful," not "pitiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我知道。\N{\rENG}- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想听听\N{\rENG}I just wanted to hear you say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我在想，\N{\rENG}- You know, I was thinking, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你可以做我的女朋友。\N{\rENG}maybe you could be my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想没有你的生活\N{\rENG}SINGER:  Didn't wanna live without you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哦，不。\N{\rENG}- Whoa, um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉，迈克。我只是——\N{\rENG}I'm--I'm sorry, Mike. I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，过去两周过得很开心，\N{\rENG}Look, the last two weeks have been really fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有很多事要做\N{\rENG}but I just got a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，机会并不多\N{\rENG}I mean, there's not a lot of opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为好莱坞的黑人女演员准备的。\N{\rENG}for Black actresses in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经22岁了。我时间不多了。\N{\rENG}I'm already 22. I don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但我有足够我们俩的钱\N{\rENG}- But I--I got enough money for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系。\N{\rENG}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这对我很重要。\N{\rENG}- It matters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经做到了。你现在是事业的巅峰。\N{\rENG}You've already made it. You're at the top of your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都盯着你。-是的。\N{\rENG}All eyes on you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:我不想活在别人的阴影里。\N{\rENG}ROBIN: I don't wanna live in someone else's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有我自己的梦想。\N{\rENG}I got my own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，迈克。\N{\rENG}I'm sorry, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手:\N{\rENG}你认为理所当然\N{\rENG}SINGER:\N{\rENG}You took for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-让我们倒带，我告诉你我听到了什么。\N{\rENG}- Let's rewind, and I'll tell you what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(磁带啸声)\N{\rENG}[tape squealing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-黑鬼，你太蠢了，太布朗斯维尔了\N{\rENG}- Nigga, you too stupid and too Brownsville
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为我的一切。\N{\rENG}to be my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的参与。\N{\rENG}Thanks for playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:但那只会让我更想要她。\N{\rENG}MIKE: But that just made me want her more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在一起玩，\N{\rENG}We were still hanging out and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这并不代表她就是我的。\N{\rENG}but that didn't make her mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她是我的。\N{\rENG}I wanted her to be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果我给她足够的东西，\N{\rENG}You know, I thought if I give her enough stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以让她爱上我。\N{\rENG}I can make her love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我对爱情一无所知。\N{\rENG}Nah, I didn't know anything about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道我在电影里看到的。\N{\rENG}I only knew what I saw in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，这就是我在玩的。\N{\rENG}You know, that's what I was playing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾坠入爱河\N{\rENG}I was in love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但以我自己的方式，对吧?\N{\rENG}but in my own kind of fucked-up way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(笑声)\N{\rENG}[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(欢快的音乐)\N{\rENG}[upbeat music]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨。\N{\rENG}- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我在找玫瑰。\N{\rENG}- I'm looking for some roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[门咔哒一声打开]\N{\rENG}[door clicks open]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- - - - - -[笑]\N{\rENG}- [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——(呻吟)\N{\rENG}- [moaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手:\N{\rENG}我不能否认\N{\rENG}SINGER:\N{\rENG}I can't deny
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我的感觉\N{\rENG}The way you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:我喜欢这个。\N{\rENG}MIKE: I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不错的选择。\N{\rENG}- Excellent choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们是南海珍珠。[笑]\N{\rENG}They're Southern Sea pearls. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(喘息)\N{\rENG}[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:也许我和那些女人在一起，因为我从来没有\N{\rENG}MIKE: Maybe I was with all those women because I never
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真以为我能搞定罗宾。\N{\rENG}really thought I could get Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者我当时才21岁，很饥渴。\N{\rENG}Or maybe I was just 21 and horny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在和罗宾的求爱过程中，\N{\rENG}Through all the courtship with Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还在战斗。\N{\rENG}I was still fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我和破骨者吵了一架。\N{\rENG}I remember I had this one fight with Bonecrusher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个特别固执的混蛋。\N{\rENG}He was a particularly hardheaded motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(普通员工)\N{\rENG}[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(铃响)\N{\rENG}[bell dings]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的是，\N{\rENG}The funny thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得《破骨者》帮我找到了罗宾。\N{\rENG}I think Bonecrusher helped me get Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:嘿。\N{\rENG}MIKE: Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨。\N{\rENG}- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了这场比赛。你还好吗?\N{\rENG}I watched the fight. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:我很好。\N{\rENG}MIKE: I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很接近。\N{\rENG}It was close, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得如果我不赢，人们就会讨厌我。\N{\rENG}I always feel like if I don't win, people will hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要挨揍才会有人喜欢我。\N{\rENG}Like, I really have to get beat up for somebody to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- - - - - -[笑]\N{\rENG}- [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你，迈克尔。\N{\rENG}I like you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:如果库斯在这里，我就有人可以说话了。\N{\rENG}MIKE: If Cus was here, I'd have somebody to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米是我唯一的亲人了。\N{\rENG}Jimmy's all I got now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我来了\N{\rENG}- Well, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我希望你在这里。\N{\rENG}- I wish you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:迈克尔…(叹息)\N{\rENG}ROBIN: Michael...[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你被打，我的心都痛了。\N{\rENG}It hurts my heart to see you get hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这让我很累。\N{\rENG}Like, it takes too much out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它真的让我生病了。\N{\rENG}It literally makes me ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我只是想保护你。\N{\rENG}But...I just wanna protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿,迈克尔?\N{\rENG}Hey, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想让我做你的女朋友吗?\N{\rENG}Do you still want me to be your girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——真的吗?\N{\rENG}- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想做我的女孩吗?\N{\rENG}You really wanna be my girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的，我知道。\N{\rENG}- Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:是吗?\N{\rENG}MIKE: Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是啊，我想你。\N{\rENG}- Yeah, I--I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要在你改变主意之前把电话挂了。\N{\rENG}- I'm gonna hang up the phone before you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有女朋友了。\N{\rENG}I got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-今晚不行，你不行。\N{\rENG}- Not tonight, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【第八天的《她不只是另一个女人》】\N{\rENG}[8th Day's "She's Not Just Another Woman"]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手:她不只是另一个女人\N{\rENG}SINGERS:  She's not just another woman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是，不，不\N{\rENG}She's not, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不只是另一个女人\N{\rENG}She's not just another woman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是，不，不\N{\rENG}She's not, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她给了我一个新生的生命\N{\rENG}She's given me a newborn birth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这苦涩的地球上找到了甜蜜\N{\rENG}I found sweetness on this bitter Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道该说什么\N{\rENG}She knows the things to say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我摆脱烦恼\N{\rENG}To help my troubles away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当她说的话行不通时\N{\rENG}And when the words she say won't do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会试着吻你一两个\N{\rENG}She'll try a kiss or two
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的，我的，我的\N{\rENG}She's mine, mine, mine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道如何安慰我\N{\rENG}She knows how to console me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的，我的，我的\N{\rENG}She's mine, mine, mine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道如何控制我\N{\rENG}She knows how to control me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让任何人谈论我的宝贝\N{\rENG}I don't want nobody talking 'bout my baby
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人谈论我的宝贝\N{\rENG}Nobody talkin' 'bout my baby
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:这是……(笑)\N{\rENG}ROBIN: This is...[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，你知道你没必要这么做，对吧?\N{\rENG}I mean, you know you didn't have to do this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是啊，但这不是那种戒指。\N{\rENG}- Yeah, well, it's not that kind of ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是结婚什么的。\N{\rENG}Not marriage or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你知道，当你准备好了，告诉我。\N{\rENG}But, you know, whenever you're ready, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你找比这更好更大的。\N{\rENG}I'll get you something way better than that, way bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-看看我们。\N{\rENG}- Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看起来很有抱负。迈克:是的。\N{\rENG}We look aspirational. MIKE: Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我是说，我没有榜样\N{\rENG}- I mean, I didn't have role models
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一样长大的人。\N{\rENG}of people who looked like us growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们就是他们。\N{\rENG}And now we're them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太令人兴奋了。\N{\rENG}It's--it's so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的。-你真令人兴奋。\N{\rENG}- Yeah. - You're so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们太兴奋了。-是的。\N{\rENG}We're so exciting. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-想想我们能激励多少人。\N{\rENG}- Think of all the people we can inspire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的。\N{\rENG}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-说到灵感…\N{\rENG}- Speaking of inspiration...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你给我带来了什么?\N{\rENG}- What you got for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫米。\N{\rENG}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(笑)好。\N{\rENG}[chuckles] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧。(手铐摇铃)\N{\rENG}Okay. [handcuffs rattle]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(有弹性的音乐)\N{\rENG}[bouncy music]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你现在是我的了，冠军。\N{\rENG}- You're mine now, champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——正确的。\N{\rENG}- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(两人都笑)\N{\rENG}[both chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(罗宾唧唧的声音)\N{\rENG}[Robin yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:那是我第一次恋爱。\N{\rENG}MIKE: It was the first time I was in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们当时只有21岁和22岁。\N{\rENG}We were only 21 and 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(两个都笑了起来)\N{\rENG}[both laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切发生得太快了。\N{\rENG}It was happening so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太快了。\N{\rENG}Too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要生孩子了?\N{\rENG}Gonna have a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米告诉我你怀孕了。\N{\rENG}Jimmy told me you're knocked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉了我的业务经理，却没告诉我?\N{\rENG}You told my business manager, but you didn't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我只告诉了我妈\N{\rENG}- I only told my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许她告诉他了?\N{\rENG}Maybe she told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想给你压力。\N{\rENG}I didn't wanna pressure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?\N{\rENG}Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的。\N{\rENG}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——是吗?-是的。\N{\rENG}- Yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澄清一下，罗宾说她怀孕了\N{\rENG}To be clear, Robin says she got pregnant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们结婚后，\N{\rENG}after we got married,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们都不会花钱去看她的演出。\N{\rENG}but y'all aren't paying to see her show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(笑声)\N{\rENG}[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了唯一觉得对的事\N{\rENG}I did the only thing that felt right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我觉得不对劲的时候。\N{\rENG}every time I thought something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更搞砸了。\N{\rENG}I fucked it up even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-直到死亡将你们分开?\N{\rENG}- Till death do you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的。\N{\rENG}- I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你跟我说我们要去看全明星赛。\N{\rENG}- You told me we were going to the All-Star Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我觉得这样更浪漫。\N{\rENG}- Well, I thought this was more romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-比篮球更浪漫?\N{\rENG}- More romantic than basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你爱我?\N{\rENG}- You love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(欢快的音乐)\N{\rENG}[upbeat music]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的。\N{\rENG}- I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧师:你可以吻新娘了。\N{\rENG}PRIEST: You may kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[欢呼和掌声]\N{\rENG}[cheers and applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(按快门)-大家放轻松。\N{\rENG}[camera shutters clicking] - Relax, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他马上就出来。\N{\rENG}He'll be out in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪。\N{\rENG}Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三得利干衣店的销售代表在盯着你，\N{\rENG}Suntory Dry Man reps have their eyes on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们得保证这次旅行干净利落，对吧?\N{\rENG}so we gotta keep this trip squeaky-clean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是一个不同的市场。\N{\rENG}It's a different market here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有坏男孩的东西。\N{\rENG}No bad-boy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要预支我的钱包。\N{\rENG}- I need an advance on my purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想从日本给罗宾买点好东西。\N{\rENG}I wanna get Robin something nice from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在罗宾身上花了很多钱。\N{\rENG}- You're spending a lot on Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要慢下来。\N{\rENG}You need to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她是我妻子。我想给她一个惊喜。\N{\rENG}- She's my wife. I wanna surprise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧，给她爱的礼物。\N{\rENG}- All right, give her the gift of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(叹息)\N{\rENG}[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，好吧，好吧。\N{\rENG}All right, all right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看我能做些什么。\N{\rENG}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么不是吉米在管钱?\N{\rENG}- Why isn't Jimmy handling the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[深吸一口气]\N{\rENG}- [inhales deeply]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧师:我们祈祷吉米·雅各布斯的灵魂\N{\rENG}PRIEST: And we pray that the soul of Jimmy Jacobs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到它永恒的归宿。\N{\rENG}find its eternal resting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是些真东西。\N{\rENG}- So here's some real shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米，我喜欢的经理，库斯挑选的，\N{\rENG}Jimmy, the manager I liked, that Cus had picked,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我病了很多年，他们都瞒着我。\N{\rENG}had been sick for years, and they hid it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯顿让我签了份合同说如果吉米死了，\N{\rENG}Cayton got me to sign some contract saying if Jimmy died,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯顿会自动成为我的经纪人。\N{\rENG}Cayton would automatically be my manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至还说要给他们的寡妇\N{\rENG}They even put some shit in about giving their widows
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的50%如果他们死了，\N{\rENG}50% of me if they died,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我是他们可以随意传递的动产\N{\rENG}like I was some chattel they could pass around...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他们拥有我一样。\N{\rENG}Like they own me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾不喜欢这样，她把他们告得屁滚尿流。\N{\rENG}Robin didn't like that, and she sued the fuck out of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手:\N{\rENG}太多改变了\N{\rENG}SINGER:\N{\rENG}So much did change
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁斯:嗯，谢谢你来见我们。\N{\rENG}RUTH: Well, thank you for meeting with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我女儿现在是迈克尔的代理律师，\N{\rENG}Since my daughter is now Michael's power of attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想看看他的账目。\N{\rENG}we'd like to see his accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我只是希望我的家庭一切都完美。\N{\rENG}- I just want everything to be perfect for my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要照顾的不只是我们。\N{\rENG}It's not just us we need to look out for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:但是罗宾负责我的财务\N{\rENG}MIKE: But with Robin doing my finances
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米突然走了\N{\rENG}and with Jimmy suddenly gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人从后门溜进来的。\N{\rENG}someone else snuck in the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堂。金:在这场巨大的悲剧中，\N{\rENG}DON KING: In this great tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去一位朋友和同事，\N{\rENG}the loss of a friend and colleague,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个机会。\N{\rENG}lays an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米没走。\N{\rENG}Jimmy isn't gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被转化为纯灵了。\N{\rENG}He's transferred into pure spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的，你和他之间的信任关系\N{\rENG}In the--in the same way, your trusting relationship with him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一定是丢了，只是调走了。\N{\rENG}doesn't have to be lost, just transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[笑]\N{\rENG}[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克，你有机会\N{\rENG}Mike, you have an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌握自己的命运。\N{\rENG}to take control of your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个完全解放的黑人，\N{\rENG}As one fully liberated Black man to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安慰自己，死亡只是一个过渡，\N{\rENG}take solace that death is but a transition,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的重生。\N{\rENG}and I am your rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[笑]\N{\rENG}[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他是个迷人的混蛋。\N{\rENG}- Oh, he's a charming motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈。\N{\rENG}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(欢快的音乐)\N{\rENG}[upbeat music]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:现在，看看巴黎的照片\N{\rENG}ROBIN: Now, the pictures from Paris
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该在星期五到达。\N{\rENG}were supposed to arrive on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白为什么要耽搁。\N{\rENG}I don't understand what the holdup is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得给克里斯托夫打个电话。\N{\rENG}You need to get on the phone with Christophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道法国人是什么样的。\N{\rENG}You know how these French people are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得控制住他们。哦,宝贝。\N{\rENG}You have to stay on top of them. Oh, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要Vulcano丝绸\N{\rENG}So I'm thinking Vulcano silk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间，然后也许…\N{\rENG}for this room and then maybe a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:每个人都认为罗宾到处乱跑\N{\rENG}MIKE: Everyone has this vision that Robin ran around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的装修师都在装修房子。\N{\rENG}with all the decorators doing the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是废话。\N{\rENG}That's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错。\N{\rENG}It was all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要她没有的。\N{\rENG}- I'll have what she's not having.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-为我们完美的新家干杯\N{\rENG}- A toast to our perfect new home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有迈克尔，他将成为最好的父亲，\N{\rENG}and to Michael, who is going to be the best father,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妈妈一直对我们照顾得那么好。\N{\rENG}and Mom for always taking such good care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露丝:你们是我的孩子。\N{\rENG}RUTH: You're my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的职责是保护你\N{\rENG}It's my job to protect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是当你甚至不知道你需要它的时候。\N{\rENG}especially when you don't even know you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是什么意思?\N{\rENG}- What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-妈，现在不行。\N{\rENG}- Mom, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你们俩都这么年轻。\N{\rENG}- You're both so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是担心那些人\N{\rENG}I'm just concerned that the people who are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本应该照顾你的，却没有。\N{\rENG}supposed to be looking out for you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——嗯…[笑]\N{\rENG}- Well... [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈想说的是…\N{\rENG}What mom is trying to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比尔·凯顿一直在偷我们的钱。\N{\rENG}Bill Cayton's been stealing from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从你。\N{\rENG}From you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——唐纳德·特朗普提供了他的咨询服务。\N{\rENG}- Donald Trump has offered his consulting services.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是你可以信任的商人。\N{\rENG}Now, that's a businessman you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你们就找不到小点的鸡吗?\N{\rENG}- You guys couldn't find a smaller chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是一只鹌鹑。\N{\rENG}- It's a quail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么是鹌鹑?\N{\rENG}- What's a quail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐:(笑)\N{\rENG}DON: [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹌鹑?该死的!\N{\rENG}Quail? Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和鸽子赛跑。你不吃它们!\N{\rENG}You race pigeons. You don't eat 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(笑)\N{\rENG}[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些女人想转化你\N{\rENG}Those women are trying to turn you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成娘娘腔。\N{\rENG}into some kind of sissy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，你就会\N{\rENG}Next thing you know, you gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝着香槟，小指举在空中!\N{\rENG}drinking Champale, pinkie in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[笑]\N{\rENG}[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小特是个温柔的白人男孩。\N{\rENG}Ooh, that Trump's a tender-handed white boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯。\N{\rENG}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这辈子都没长过老茧。\N{\rENG}Never had a callus in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的钱是他爸爸给的。\N{\rENG}Got his money from his daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在软化你。\N{\rENG}They're softening you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的蛋蛋在她手里。妈妈想要把他们割下来。\N{\rENG}Girl's got your balls. Mama's lookin' to cut 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那是我老婆\N{\rENG}- Man, that's my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——(呻吟)\N{\rENG}- [groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个不在乎的人就会闭嘴，\N{\rENG}Someone who didn't care would shut the fuck up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也别说。\N{\rENG}not say a goddamn word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能眼睁睁看着冠军变成笨蛋。\N{\rENG}But I can't stand by and watch the champ become a chump.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫米毫米,嗯。\N{\rENG}Mm-mm, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着国王，孩子，你会没事的。\N{\rENG}Stick with the King, boy, you'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[笑]\N{\rENG}[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:唐说对了一件事。\N{\rENG}MIKE: That's one thing Don was right about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露丝和罗宾抓住了我的蛋蛋。\N{\rENG}Ruth and Robin had me by the balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我和我的蛋蛋开始减少在家的时间。\N{\rENG}So me and my balls started spending less time at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:(鼓掌两次)\N{\rENG}ROBIN: [claps twice]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是凌晨四点。\N{\rENG}It's 4:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我以为你睡着了。\N{\rENG}- I thought you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我猜你也有\N{\rENG}- Mm, I bet you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——嗯。\N{\rENG}- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你去哪儿了?\N{\rENG}- Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我是说我…我是说…\N{\rENG}- I mean, I was, um-- I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和唐在一起。\N{\rENG}I was with Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的。-真的吗?\N{\rENG}Yeah. - Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是唐的颜色吗?\N{\rENG}Is that Don's color?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧，我不用告诉你\N{\rENG}- Okay, I don't have to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去过哪里，和谁在一起，好吗?\N{\rENG}where I've been or who I've been with, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-[嘲笑]天啊，迈克，\N{\rENG}- [scoffs] Jesus, Mike,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟我爸干的一模一样!\N{\rENG}this is the same shit my dad did, the same shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我警告过你。\N{\rENG}I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-警告我?-是的。\N{\rENG}- Warned me? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-听着，你和你妈妈不能变成冠军\N{\rENG}- Listen, you and your mother can't turn the champ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成笨蛋，好吗?\N{\rENG}into a chump, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在说什么?\N{\rENG}- What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你根本不在乎我。\N{\rENG}- You don't care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只关心花我的钱。\N{\rENG}All you care about is spending my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我是想保护你\N{\rENG}- I'm trying to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从偷你钱的人那里。\N{\rENG}from people who are stealing your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这样你就可以花了。\N{\rENG}- So you can spend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:我要把钱花在你身上。\N{\rENG}ROBIN: I'm spending it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白我们需要一切都完美无缺\N{\rENG}You don't understand that we need everything to be perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为每个人都在看。\N{\rENG}because everyone is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么做?\N{\rENG}And what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出轨的程度比我爸还严重。\N{\rENG}You go out and you're cheating worse than my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我真希望你没怀孕\N{\rENG}- You know, I wish you weren't pregnant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就不用和你结婚了\N{\rENG}so I wouldn't have had to get married to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你的愿望实现了，迈克尔\N{\rENG}- Well, you got your wish, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那时她告诉我她把孩子弄丢了。\N{\rENG}- That's when she told me she lost the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾说她在医院把孩子弄丢了\N{\rENG}Robin said she lost the baby in the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她在一起\N{\rENG}and I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道。\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她写了她的书，我写了我的。\N{\rENG}She wrote her book, and I wrote mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道，我想要那种梦幻般的生活\N{\rENG}What I do know is, I wanted that fantasy life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了罗宾，我什么都愿意给她。\N{\rENG}for Robin so bad, I would've given her anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，几乎任何事情。\N{\rENG}Well, almost anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(门铃响了)\N{\rENG}[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡米尔:迈克尔!\N{\rENG}CAMILLE: Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:见到你真高兴!\N{\rENG}[squeals] MIKE: It's so good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- - - - - -[笑]\N{\rENG}- [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦!\N{\rENG}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来不错，我的帅哥。\N{\rENG}Oh, you look good, my handsome boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢。\N{\rENG}- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你见见我美丽的，\N{\rENG}I want you to meet my beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惊人的罗宾…和露丝。\N{\rENG}stunning Robin... and Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你本人更可爱。\N{\rENG}- And you are so much more lovely in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(咯咯地笑)罗宾:哦，天哪。\N{\rENG}[giggles] ROBIN: Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡米尔:我特意为你做了肉汁。\N{\rENG}CAMILLE: I made extra gravy just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢，卡米尔。\N{\rENG}- Thanks, Camille.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露丝:[深吸一口气]\N{\rENG}RUTH: [inhales deeply]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的家真漂亮，卡米尔。\N{\rENG}Uh, you have such a beautiful home, Camille.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个放着迈克尔所有奖项和奖章的房间，\N{\rENG}That room with all of Michael's awards and, uh, medals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它就像一个神殿。\N{\rENG}it's like a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想威少是真的爱——迈克:因为。\N{\rENG}I guess Russ really did love-- MIKE: Cus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫库斯。\N{\rENG}His name is Cus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露丝:对。\N{\rENG}RUTH: Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想库斯真的很爱迈克尔。\N{\rENG}I guess Cus really loved Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡米尔:嗯，每个人都喜欢迈克尔，\N{\rENG}CAMILLE: Well, everyone loves Michael,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是客户。\N{\rENG}especially Cus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为迈克尔在拳击场上的出色表现感到骄傲。\N{\rENG}He was so proud of how great Michael was in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使在床上，他也会谈论他。\N{\rENG}Even in bed, he talks about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[笑]\N{\rENG}[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我最伟大的创造，”他说。\N{\rENG}"My greatest creation," he'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(餐具无比的)\N{\rENG}[cutlery clinking]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-太有意思了。\N{\rENG}- Just so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想，鉴于迈克尔是上帝最伟大的创造，\N{\rENG}I guess, given that Michael is Cus' greatest creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他为你的房子买单可以吗?\N{\rENG}it's okay for him to be paying for your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我——迈克:罗宾。\N{\rENG}- I-- MIKE: Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:不，我——我很抱歉。\N{\rENG}ROBIN: No, I'm--I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道为什么…\N{\rENG}I'm just wondering why it is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫在外面\N{\rENG}my husband is out there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拳击场上摧毁他的身体\N{\rENG}destroying his body in the ring
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时，用我们的钱\N{\rENG}and, meanwhile, using our money
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为这里的一切买单。\N{\rENG}to pay for everything in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,——罗宾。ROBIN:[笑]\N{\rENG}- Robin. ROBIN: [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这似乎是永无止境的\N{\rENG}And it seems to just be never-end--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[手碰桌子]\N{\rENG}[hand bangs on table]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(板咔嗒咔嗒声)\N{\rENG}[plate rattling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(手砰砰声)\N{\rENG}[hand thuds]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:你怎么了?\N{\rENG}MIKE: What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你得看看里面发生了什么。\N{\rENG}- You need to see what's going on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克:那边那位女士是我的——罗宾:你的什么?\N{\rENG}MIKE: That lady in there's my-- ROBIN: Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是你的家人。\N{\rENG}She's not your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他利用了你。——没有。\N{\rENG}Cus used you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗宾:她在利用你。——没有。\N{\rENG}ROBIN: She's using you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们伤害了你，而你，你是\N{\rENG}- They damaged you, and you're--you're, what,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你付钱给他们?\N{\rENG}you're paying them for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太渴望有人爱你了\N{\rENG}You're so desperate for someone to love you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会重写故事，只为让你感受到爱。\N{\rENG}that you'll rewrite the story just so you feel love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我的故事呢?\N{\rENG}But--but what about my story?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你，你却因此恨我。\N{\rENG}I love you, and you hate me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身边没有人，所以你让克劳斯转化了你\N{\rENG}You didn't have anyone, so you let Cus turn you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成了他的野兽，现在你却在这里\N{\rENG}into his brute, and now you're out here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为这个白人老太太的房子买单，\N{\rENG}paying for this old white lady's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像雇工一样给她修剪草坪。\N{\rENG}mowing her lawn like the hired help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么?\N{\rENG}And for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她给你额外的肉汁还冲你笑?\N{\rENG}Because she gives you extra gravy and smiles at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么天真。\N{\rENG}Don't be so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-管好你的嘴，贱人\N{\rENG}- You watch your mouth, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哦，真有趣。\N{\rENG}- Oh, that's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一分钟前，你还叫我宝贝。\N{\rENG}Just a minute ago, you were calling me baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我说真的，罗宾我——\N{\rENG}- I mean it, Robin. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(咆哮)\N{\rENG}[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(拳头重击声)\N{\rENG}[fist thuds]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎么拼才会输，只会赢。\N{\rENG}I don't know how to fight to lose, only to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道如何去爱赢。\N{\rENG}I don't know how to love to win either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[比尔·威瑟斯的《美好的一天》]\N{\rENG}[Bill Withers' "Lovely Day"]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生:锂应该有助于稳定\N{\rENG}DOCTOR: The lithium should help stabilize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的情绪和行为。\N{\rENG}your moods and behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-药物通常不会让我更稳定。\N{\rENG}- Pills don't usually make me more stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生:躁狂抑郁症是一场终生的战斗，迈克。\N{\rENG}DOCTOR: Manic depression is a lifelong battle, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很幸运有这么好的支持系统。\N{\rENG}You're lucky to have such a great support system.
